name: Men's 'Outlaw' Boots (Sansha's Nation)
description:
Designer: Unknown

Straight from the discreet consignments of Intaki Commerce, these boots indicate that the wearer is a true supporter of the Sansha cause. These tall lace-up boots make a statement of power and dominance in olive and charcoal gray. When paired with the matching jacket and pants, these boots represent the ultimate homage to Sansha's Nation.
